":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T13:33:51.000Z","msg":"非法傾銷"},{"pid":"5b991ee513c5eb466b961d76993d6380262efdb2","tid":864821,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T13:36:04.000Z","msg":"雖則慳左人工錢<br />\n但扣翻運費<br />\n一分錢一分貨<br />\n<br />\n品質邊隻優良好明顯"},{"pid":"c1a6006f8e4ed485a42b3cbac578c90d4eba9cc7","tid":864821,"uid":162272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T13:40:04.000Z","msg":"生產一箱大蒜大約30美元，我們或許可以賣出35美元，但中國以10美元一箱傾銷美國市場，低於他們的生產花費。川普當局對2000億美元中國進口產品加徵關稅，最初的稅率為10%。從2019年1月1日開始，將提高至25%。<br />\n<br />\n就算加徵25%關稅後, $10 x 1.25 = $12.5, 買佢一盒嘅錢仲夠買人地三盒。係咪有數據報錯左?"},{"pid":"7190df948154d4db7a87ea062967c3c0ea0bccb2","tid":864821,"uid":33481,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T13:42:34.000Z","msg":"加州變replicaian就真係變天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9099d1c0059dedb87e3238dfce4587d9a774af2","tid":864821,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T13:43:21.000Z","msg":"Go侵go<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2724fe904115d596e1833314f250d03a2ea5f4f3","tid":864821,"uid":50984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7190df948154d4db7a87ea062967c3c0ea0bccb2","tid":864821,"uid":33481,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T13:42:34.000Z","msg":"加州變replicaian就真係變天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T13:44:52.000Z","msg":"左膠州份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e316328c03a02534119e22c74d945f609053b1ec","tid":864821,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T13:45:47.000Z","msg":"磨菇仔又呃鳩人"},{"pid":"80f127b22b80a3dfd32eff2503af3915f35da11a","tid":864821,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T13:47:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d95ec429e91314a43b2bcc68bdb37b6d364e5